---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Benjamin Meixner">
<section class="maya-hero">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="maya-intro-layout">
                        <div class="maya-text-content">
                            <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6 text-gray-900">About Benjamin Meixner: My Journey to LanguageBuddy</h1>
                            <p class="intro-text">
                                Hello! I'm Benjamin Meixner, an undergraduate student passionate about economics and computer science, hailing from Vienna, Austria. My personal journey learning Spanish ignited the spark for LanguageBuddy. I believe that learning a new language should be an engaging, effective, and accessible experience for everyone. LanguageBuddy, or Maya as I affectionately call our AI, is born from this belief—a tool I initially created for myself and now wish to share with the world. My vision is to empower language learners globally, transforming the often-frustrating process into a seamless, conversational adventure.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

        <section class="py-16 bg-bg-light">
            <div class="container flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
                <div class="md:w-1/2 p-8 rounded-lg">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">The Challenge I Faced</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg mb-4">When preparing for my exchange semester in Peru, I needed to learn Spanish rapidly. Traditional methods, however, left me uninspired:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg mb-4 text-gray-700">
                        <li><strong class="text-primary">Traditional Courses:</strong> Difficult to prepare for lessons, review grammar, and lacked practical application, leading to low motivation.</li>
                        <li><strong class="text-primary">Flashcards (Anki):</strong> Useful for rote memorization (like irregular verbs) but quickly became boring and ineffective for genuine language acquisition.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="text-lg mb-8">I yearned for real conversation, for a way to actively use the language and cement my understanding.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2 text-center">
                    <img 
                        src="/ceo_benjamin_colca.jpeg" 
                        alt="Benjamin Meixner in Colca Canyon" 
                        class="mx-auto rounded-lg shadow-xl max-w-lg w-full object-cover maya-image-ceo"
                    />
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-base italic mt-2">Colca Canyon, Arequipa, Peru, September 2025</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="py-16">
            <div class="container flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-8">
                <div class="md:w-1/2 p-8 rounded-lg">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">The LLM Revelation</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg mb-4">A turning point came when I started experimenting with Large Language Models (LLMs). Finally, I was forming sentences, actively communicating, and striving to get my point across. It was a game-changer! However, this approach also presented its own set of frustrations:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg mb-4 text-gray-700">
                        <li><strong class="text-primary">Cumbersome Setup:</strong> Constantly opening new chats, finding specific prompts to configure the LLM's behavior.</li>
                        <li><strong class="text-primary">Inconsistent Behavior:</strong> The LLM often didn't act exactly as desired, requiring constant oversight.</li>
                        <li><strong class="text-primary">Lack of Persistence:</strong> No memory of past conversations or reminders to continue practicing.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="text-lg mb-4">My daily routine involved WhatsApp, my goal was effective LLM practice, but the tools at hand were disjointed and forgetful.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2 text-center">
                    <img 
                        src="/ceo_benjamin_surf.jpeg" 
                        alt="Benjamin Meixner surfing" 
                        class="mx-auto rounded-lg shadow-xl max-w-lg w-full object-cover maya-image-ceo"
                    />
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-base italic mt-2">Makaha, Lima, October 2025</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="py-16 bg-bg-light">
            <div class="container flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
                <div class="md:w-1/2 p-8 rounded-lg">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">My Solution: Building LanguageBuddy</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg mb-4">Driven by these challenges, I began to build my own solution: a simple service connected to WhatsApp, leveraging a sophisticated system prompt to ChatGPT. What started as a personal project, a "small service," evolved significantly:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg mb-4 text-gray-700">
                        <li><strong class="text-primary">Seamless Integration:</strong> Direct interaction through WhatsApp, a platform I use daily.</li>
                        <li><strong class="text-primary">Refined AI Behavior:</strong> Months of refining system prompts to ensure the AI (Maya) behaved exactly as I needed for effective language practice.</li>
                        <li><strong class="text-primary">Feature Expansion:</strong> Gradually adding features that enhanced the learning experience.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="text-lg mb-4">This personal tool allowed me to achieve conversational fluency in Spanish within five months—a success I attribute largely to Maya.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2 text-center">
                    <img 
                        src="/ceo_benjamin_mate.jpeg" 
                        alt="Benjamin Meixner drinking mate" 
                        class="mx-auto rounded-lg shadow-xl max-w-lg w-full object-cover maya-image-ceo"
                    />
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-base italic mt-2">Machachi, Ecuador, November 2025</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="py-16 text-center">
            <div class="container max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 p-8 rounded-lg">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900">Join My Vision</h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">The positive feedback from friends and even my former Spanish tutor encouraged me to offer this tool to others. My goal is to provide you with the same invaluable resource that transformed my Spanish learning journey. Maya taught me so much, and I am confident she will accompany you on many language adventures. Spanish was just the beginning for me, and it won't be the last journey she helps me with.</p>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Join me in embracing a new, more natural way to learn languages.</p>
                <a 
                    href="https://wa.me/436802456552" 
                    target="_blank" 
                    rel="noopener noreferrer" 
                    class="btn btn-whatsapp"
                >
                    Contact me on WhatsApp
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <style>
            .maya-hero {
                background-color: var(--bg);
                padding: 4rem 0 6rem 0;
                color: var(--text);
            }

            .maya-intro-layout {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                gap: 4rem;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
            }

            .maya-image-container {
                flex: 0 0 auto;
            }

            .maya-text-content {
                flex: 1;
                max-width: 600px;
            }

            .maya-hero h1 {
                font-size: 3.5rem;
                margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
                color: var(--text); /* Changed to var(--text) for consistency */
                line-height: 1.1;
            }

            .intro-text {
                font-size: 1.25rem;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: var(--text-light);
                margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            }

            .maya-image-ceo {
                max-height: 400px; /* Consistent image height */
            }

            /* Responsive adjustments */
            @media (max-width: 900px) {
                .maya-intro-layout {
                    flex-direction: column;
                    text-align: center;
                    gap: 2rem;
                }

                .maya-text-content {
                    display: flex;
                    flex-direction: column;
                    align-items: center;
                }
                
                .maya-hero h1 {
                    font-size: 2.5rem;
                }
            }
        </style>
